---
title: Grilled Jerk Chicken Burgers with Sweet Potato Wedges and Chili Mayo Dipper
description: Fun and fiery Caribbean flavours are here to tickle your tastebuds. Smoky jerk sauce marinated chicken patties and crisp and cooling coleslaw are  stacked together on a toasted burger bun. On the side, tuck into sweet potato fries and a chili mayo dipper.
